      "short": "",
      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>Drow gain the following spell-like abilities. The caster level for these effects is equal to the drow’s level.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>At will&nbsp;</strong><em>@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.spells.Item.rSWg5JnN3mxzkatD]{Dancing Lights}, @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.spells.Item.kxx5x0JAgFuEQJAm]{Detect Magic}</em></li>\n</ul>\n<p>In addition, drow count as having the @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.feats.Item.ci82dXIp6UtcluEE]{Minor Psychic Power} feat for the purpose of meeting prerequisites, and if a drow takes the @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.feats.Item.5a0a2zXORbPi09Hu]{Psychic Power} feat, she can add the drow noble’s @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.racial-features.Item.SsL6aUIEvJp0sNML]{Limning Light} supernatural ability to the list of spell-like abilities available to her.</p>"
